{"tid":861893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"31歲小學女老師、兼職女模　被指控性侵10歲男學生","createTime":"2018-10-14T12:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T14:34:39.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"798bc4c238ea2e8366a97133a85359df7459b115","tid":861893,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:48:21.000Z","msg":"一名31歲小學老師、兼職女模，被指控對一名十歲學生性侵。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《metro》報導，加拿大31歲女老師威爾森(Krystal Wilson)，2017年到2018年在安大略省地達文西公立學校(Da Vinci Public School)任教時，性侵一名十歲男學生，被控兩項性侵罪以及兩項性騷擾罪。<br />\n<br />\n威爾森過去曾擔任模特兒以及歌手，還在電台上進行宣傳，她之前還接受採訪，稱她對教學以及音樂有相當大的熱情，「我很幸運能成為一名小學老師，這讓我不僅能夠指導這些年輕人，還可以跟他們分享我對藝術的熱情」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"6e8d4c8a1505d33dae442971542b2882821dc41f","tid":861893,"uid":131033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"快點"},{"pid":"013aa6e884c69718d99f6be62f61648ace8c41fe","tid":861893,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:50:29.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"04371b51caeeb9943330eb87070cc8121f768798","tid":861893,"uid":66604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"留個名先"},{"pid":"c0433ab14f0c59a5f634ecdf106b51ef54cb36c0","tid":861893,"uid":48570,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:53:54.000Z","msg":"貼咗相先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59677ee785331f8e3289445829da6947ba2a441","tid":861893,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e8d4c8a1505d33dae442971542b2882821dc41f","tid":861893,"uid":131033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"快點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:55:30.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂"},{"pid":"7ab6650f702da19a6fe80b3a3978057fb2c73a52","tid":861893,"uid":55657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"h